%define OT_LeastSquaresMethod_solve_doc
"Solve the least-squares problem.

.. math::

    \vect{a} = \argmin_{\vect{x} \in \Rset^P} ||M\vect{x}-\vect{b}||^2

Parameters
----------
b : sequence of float
    Second term of the equation

Returns
-------
a : :class:`~openturns.Point`
    The solution."
%enddef
